Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后然后  五班有个超可爱的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女生有那么一点点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏目  你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我在听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那双清澈的眼睛直直的看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字不知道  因为她一句话都不说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里  夏目？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说五班有个可爱女生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  赶快走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么夏目也要去？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走快点走快点  休息时间要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…啊  有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她  是她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  感觉好像有点阴沉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是看点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  站起来了  要出来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是二班的西村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟你做个朋友啊…之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  她的确是看着我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗  你多心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:19.19,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(837,254)}少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:19.19,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(902,432)}女
